@host = http://localhost:5007

### Health — reports mode, chunkCount, embeddingDimensions
GET {{host}}/health

###

### Ask — standard RAG pipeline (retrieve + rerank + grounded generation)
POST {{host}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Qual o termo inicial da prescricao intercorrente na execucao fiscal?"
}

###

### Ask — out-of-domain query triggers refusal (anti-hallucination path)
POST {{host}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Qual a capital da Australia?"
}

###

### Ask/CRAG — corrective RAG: grades retrieval, re-queries when weak
POST {{host}}/ask/crag
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "gostaria de saber sobre a prescricao intercorrente na execucao fiscal"
}

###

### Ask/Agentic — SK plugin invoked via M.E.AI function-invocation loop (keyless)
POST {{host}}/ask/agentic
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "O que diz a Sumula 435 do STJ sobre redirecionamento na execucao fiscal?"
}

###

### Ingest text — index a plain-text document
POST {{host}}/ingest/text
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceFile": "sample-doc.txt",
  "content": "Sumula 106 STJ: Proposta a acao no prazo fixado para o seu exercicio, a demora na citacao, por motivos inerentes ao mecanismo da Justica, nao justifica o acolhimento da arguicao de prescricao ou decadencia."
}

###

### Eval — deterministic gate: lexical faithfulness, citation correctness, refusal accuracy
POST {{host}}/eval

###

### Eval/Retrieval — Recall@K / Hit-rate@K / MRR over the golden set
POST {{host}}/eval/retrieval

###

### Eval/Ablation — compares dense-only / sparse-only / hybrid / hybrid+rerank
POST {{host}}/eval/ablation

###

### Eval/Perturbation — hit-rate delta across surface-form variants (casing, whitespace, term order)
POST {{host}}/eval/perturbation
